Class UISocketVariable

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wisc.trace.uch.util.socket.AbstractUISocketElement

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IUISocketElement

    public class UISocketVariable
extends AbstractUISocketElement
    UISocketVariable is the variable variant of UISocketElement. It provides the functionality to set and get the variable value.
